metadata.name: EloiseLavinie #001
metadata.description:
A story of a young girl that felt everything the world has to offer. She trusted, believed, closed her eyes and flew where colors have meaning. Where sound is an echo filled with pinks and blues.

"Don't believe what you see because truths are hidden where you are blind", she says. 

A journey inside Eloise Lavinie's mind. Have a nice trip.
